                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <div class="trust-icon-box me-4 flex-shrink-0" style="background: var(--neo-blue); color: white;">
                            <i class="bi bi-award"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="fw-bold text-uppercase">Certified</h4>
                            <p class="small fw-bold text-muted">Get recognized certifications that employers actually value.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <div class="trust-icon-box me-4 flex-shrink-0" style="background: var(--neo-orange); color: white;">
                            <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="fw-bold text-uppercase">Mentorship</h4>
                            <p class="small fw-bold text-muted">1-on-1 guidance from senior engineers at top tech companies.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <div class="trust-icon-box me-4 flex-shrink-0" style="background: #000; color: white;">
                            <i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="fw-bold text-uppercase">Career Launch</h4>
                            <p class="small fw-bold text-muted">Resume reviews, mock interviews, and direct hiring partner referrals.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Newsletter / CTA -->
<section class="py-5" style="background: var(--neo-blue); border-top: var(--neo-border);">
    <div class="container text-center text-white py-4">
        <h2 class="display-4 fw-black text-uppercase mb-3" style="font-weight: 900;">Ready to Start?</h2>
        <p class="lead fw-bold mb-4">Join the next cohort and transform your career.</p>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control p-3 fw-bold" placeholder="ENTER YOUR EMAIL" style="border: var(--neo-border); border-radius: 0;">
                    <button class="btn neo-btn" style="background: var(--neo-yellow); color: #000; border-left: none;" type="button">GET SYLLABUS</button>
